title: G3 Supp main LF ADC main duo pref Gold+
body:
I main Nami and Morg, I'm in gold 3, and I'm looking for an ADC to duo with that has lane synergy with me, add me if you're interested, we will play a practice game and see how we work together. :) Must be willing to communicate and listen. 

- CandySlay3r

Hey I was g4 last season would be more than happy to duo with you also we can do our provisional together if you want
